{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"report-to","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Security-Policy/report-to","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><dfn><code>Report-To</code></dfn>&nbsp;HTTP 响应头部指示客户端存储特定域名的报告端点。</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">Content-Security-Policy: ...; report-to groupname\n</pre>\n\n<p>该指令本身没有任何影响，仅与其他指令结合起来才有意义。</p>\n\n<table>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">CSP version</th>\n   <td>1</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">指令类型</th>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Reporting_directive\">Reporting directive <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th colspan=\"2\" scope=\"row\">\n    <p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meta\"><code>&lt;meta&gt;</code></a>&nbsp;元素并不支持该指令</p>\n   </th>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">Content-Security-Policy: report-to &lt;json-field-value&gt;;</pre>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Examples","id":"examples","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"http.headers.csp.report-to","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>可以查看<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Security-Policy-Report-Only\"><code>Content-Security-Policy-Report-Only</code></a>获取更多信息和示例。</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\"><a href=\"http://wicg.github.io/reporting/#report-to\" id=\"ref-for-report-to①\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Report-To</a>: { \"<a href=\"http://wicg.github.io/reporting/#group\" id=\"ref-for-group①\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">group</a>\": \"csp-endpoint\",\n             \"<a href=\"http://wicg.github.io/reporting/#max-age\" id=\"ref-for